{"tid":719309,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【殺過海】旺角擬撤行人專用區　表演者現身銅鑼現街頭","createTime":"2018-06-27T10:25:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T12:29:10.000Z","uid":53304,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7b92c64845c3d46076b221dbd4d16c714acbbb7b","tid":719309,"uid":53304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T10:25:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180627/s00001/87145e77e3b9bb33bc88138e385cc603.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180627%2Fs00001%2F87145e77e3b9bb33bc88138e385cc603.jpg&h=d0e72f01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖2之1 - 有表演者現身銅鑼灣街頭。（突發事故報料區成員Stanley Chow提供）<br />\n<br />\n「殺街」取消旺角行人專用區。有表演者事後表明，將會改到其他地方繼續定期演出。目前「殺街」一事未正式落實，facebook突發事故報料區群組成員Stanley Chow&lrm;昨晚已發布兩張圖片，顯示有人開始在銅鑼灣東角道表演。<br />\n<br />\n兩張相攝於銅鑼崇光百貨東角道入口對面，見有兩名女子架起平板電腦展示歌譜，在旁置有一台喇叭播放音樂高歌，咪架上有張紙上寫着「多謝支持」，安排與旺角行人專用區表演者如出一轍。<br />\n<br />\n原帖寫道：「小喇叭大媽終於侵襲銅鑼灣東角道。」有網民留言說「唔出奇」，估計旺角街人專用區取消後，陸陸續續會有更多表演者在香港其他地方現身：「唔係銅鑼灣，就係天星碼頭。」<br />\n<br />\n除了在帖中表示「我是憤怒」之外，Stanley Chow另外向記者表示，不想表演者噪音滋擾到居民：「我想多啲人關注，唔好畀佢哋搞到好似西洋菜南街咁烏煙瘴氣！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180627/s00001/8718bd470e6e300ad7ccc6622c027764.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180627%2Fs00001%2F8718bd470e6e300ad7ccc6622c027764.jpg&h=a7db21bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖2之2 - 有表演者現身銅鑼灣街頭。（突發事故報料區成員Stanley Chow提供）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180627/s00001/1530094134039\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180627%2Fs00001%2F1530094134039&d=sdiwd3qVr6FK2OrUAZn90KS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=b5c057b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180627%2Fs00001%2F1530094134039&h=d34c8214\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180627/s00001/1530094134039</a>"},{"pid":"a4e5d449cc271930c4f9acf4820a08556bc81a33","tid":719309,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T10:32:24.000Z","msg":"耳根清靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46fb4f2d4ba8c05cdfca95a35cce0fcc6b4a5101","tid":719309,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T10:44:36.000Z","msg":"好事呀"},{"pid":"b66ffe44bc501dd3789162f4c09ba163dbe675b0","tid":719309,"uid":154537,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T10:59:13.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求立法禁止班大媽街頭表演<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe392de4278bb94430fbc9f0864f5ad78747f27","tid":719309,"uid":13160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:02:38.000Z","msg":"立法唔比收錢就ok"},{"pid":"0f74b1b1cf774bb775c87645f5827e3ce59c9416","tid":719309,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:43:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180627/s00001/87145e77e3b9bb33bc88138e385cc603.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180627%2Fs00001%2F87145e77e3b9bb33bc88138e385cc603.jpg&h=d0e72f01&s={SIZE}\" />對腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cba8c3be157bafb5dd73934747576b5b6d3e391","tid":719309,"uid":10680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:50:11.000Z","msg"